  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/CoreAudioTypes\/kAudioChannelLayoutTag_AC3_3_0_1\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T14:47:46Z\n---\n\n# kAudioChannelLayoutTag_AC3_3_0_1\n\n**Global Variable**\n\nAn AC-3 layout.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvar kAudioChannelLayoutTag_AC3_3_0_1: AudioChannelLayoutTag { get }\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nYour channels must be laid out in the following order:\n\n- Left\n- Center\n- Right\n- Low-frequency effects\n\n## AC3 Defined Layouts\n\n- **kAudioChannelLayoutTag_AC3_1_0_1**: An AC-3 layout.\n- **kAudioChannelLayoutTag_AC3_3_0**: An AC-3 layout.\n- **kAudioChannelLayoutTag_AC3_3_1**: An AC-3 layout.\n- **kAudioChannelLayoutTag_AC3_2_1_1**: An AC-3 layout.\n- **kAudioChannelLayoutTag_AC3_3_1_1**: An AC-3 layout.\n\n",
